Look up the historical value of a US Dollar in Hungarian Forints

get_usdhufs.Rd

Look up the historical value of a US Dollar in Hungarian Forints

get_usdhufs(start_date = Sys.Date() - 30, end_date = Sys.Date(), retried = 0)

Arguments

start_date

date
end_date

date
retried

number of times the function has been retried

Value

data.table object
